# --- Data: license-sensitive ----------------------------------------------
# WikiHow source is CC BY-NC-SA 3.0; the corpus is released by *rehydration*
# (Myanmar text + source URLs + the build script), never by mirroring the
# English WikiHow text. So the parallel files stay out of the public repo.
data/raw/
data/processed/*.jsonl
# A 20-row teaser (data/sample/) and the aggregate stats JSONs ARE committed.

